  <th style="padding:8px;text-align:left;font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px">Details</th>
</tr></thead>
<tbody>
    <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)">
      <td style="padding:8px;font-size:13px"><a href="https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMivwFBVV95cUxOdDZhbTdkTjIya0F6RFJYZVQ2Z1gydERXdWt0anFWcUwwSjBFSDhQQUtfbU9ZaUtEaWVlalFiVS1GdWRJVzFmVmF0eWxaY3VUd2NsSkdfSXFmLTFqUnY0ZDZmaDZFMjFRQlFFeWtrOXIxTUlYSlA5a1lsNTJXZ2J1UlFRalZCTFhvSzM1MGhkVDBrVnFNVmRsVHloSG03Y2lLZjQtT0F5T1FQVHJoaThWYUpMa3ZabU43V2F0VHV5Zw?oc=5" target="_blank" style="color:var(--accent);font-weight:600">Moving Archer Forward</a></td>
      <td style="padding:8px;font-size:12px"><span style="background:var(--badge-bg, #2d3250);padding:2px 8px;border-radius:8px;font-size:10px;white-space:nowrap">Active — Community Input</span></td>
      <td style="padding:8px;font-size:12px;color:var(--text-secondary)">Complete Streets redesign for Archer Avenue: bike lanes, pedestrian safety, streetscaping. City Council review underway.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)">
      <td style="padding:8px;font-size:13px"><a href="https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiwgFBVV95cUxPdHJJMkJsTlZoTjFmNVdDRWhZYXN0YklUZjlvM3RqZ1QxLVpXbFljd3JSaVhMZ2NkRDJwWnhCaWRPSzhQVENuUXNzcm9nbmxwdjBwZ3ExN1FyR3JQTG01VFNreUhHNFZycW84bnNaRjQwRkdIYi1jS0pQQTdhZnVYYVlSaTBpbGE2QWNRRml0alJMRlQwM2RQbTJ0c0xZTmN1eVN2cVpPYXJFWEJXaFU1VzdjVDhqVU04X1VTV1d5b1V1Zw?oc=5" target="_blank" style="color:var(--accent);font-weight:600">Greater Chicago Food Depository</a></td>
      <td style="padding:8px;font-size:12px"><span style="background:var(--badge-bg, #2d3250);padding:2px 8px;border-radius:8px;font-size:10px;white-space:nowrap">Under Construction</span></td>
      <td style="padding:8px;font-size:12px;color:var(--text-secondary)">New 250,000 sq ft distribution facility near Midway. Groundbreaking held, bringing 100+ jobs to 60632 corridor.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)">
      <td style="padding:8px;font-size:13px"><a href="https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMieEFVX3lxTE1mQllDQjJwUzhGS0tFcHM0a2pXRW9jYng2UUlNSG5jU3hQQjJpdmwtRFZrZGFnUDdiaUpYWWFfcHB2N1l0MFE5M0NpMGZSQms4VGFKOXAxQmtHX3NvblVDTzlORVVBVF9XVHJBR3F1SjRxb2ZPSWtldQ?oc=5" target="_blank" style="color:var(--accent);font-weight:600">Crawford Power Plant Redevelopment</a></td>
      <td style="padding:8px;font-size:12px"><span style="background:var(--badge-bg, #2d3250);padding:2px 8px;border-radius:8px;font-size:10px;white-space:nowrap">Planning Phase</span></td>
      <td style="padding:8px;font-size:12px;color:var(--text-secondary)">Former coal plant site in Little Village — environmental remediation and mixed-use redevelopment discussions ongoing.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)">
      <td style="padding:8px;font-size:13px"><a href="https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMid0FVX3lxTE9CdXdpcktBLTVEbVNWNXd6REZISzM5MVg1VEpvT2lkbWliV21ReEczYWl1Y01iR0stNjdVQXhoNHUtNFNYRjVBUFU4WmFYNEZHSG9vQndqU0ZfLUdZcnN2YUo1Z0J5RlF2NHZnTzN1LWhyQzQ4U3dj?oc=5" target="_blank" style="color:var(--accent);font-weight:600">Midway Airport Expansion</a></td>
