<h2 style="font-size:16px;font-weight:700;margin:24px 0 8px;padding-bottom:6px;border-bottom:2px solid var(--accent);color:var(--text-primary)">Business & Employment Opportunities</h2>

<div style="margin:12px 0 20px">
<ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0">
  <li style="margin-bottom:12px;padding-left:16px;border-left:3px solid #10b981">
    <strong>Manufacturing &amp; Industrial</strong><br>
    <span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-secondary)">
      Careers in Manufacturing Program (CMP) connects high school students to Chicago manufacturing jobs. 
      Major employers in the corridor include food processing, logistics, and aviation support near Midway. 
      Wage range: \$18–\$32/hr for entry-level industrial roles.
    </span>
    <div style="margin-top:4px"><a href="https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMivwFBVV95cUxPVDdsS3ZTZC1fc0paZVdlSGNXWEVGZzV6b0RmTzUzQmtPc1lxUmRsWTR2cGRDaHhTSDdqUUtUdXhYSGlUZjE5Rm14Y2ZKejR4LV9pMVBSbmlGTnpOSTRxbXU4a2lHaHFLUnpZcU1NcHI2cDJuaWR6WVJIUTJPREVyTHEycVVGZFMtWUtBQkduX0czaXhObHdDczkyclZiODB5NlpNNGpBX29wbVhaZDRIU3NfQS02c1FEbks5bjV2OA?oc=5" target="_blank" style="color:var(--accent)">Manufacturing jobs in Chicago get a spotlight through a program for high school students - Chicago Sun-Times</a></div>
  </li>
  <li style="margin-bottom:12px;padding-left:16px;border-left:3px solid #f59e0b">
    <strong>Warehouse &amp; Logistics Hiring</strong><br>
    <span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-secondary)">
      Target warehouse in Little Village, Amazon facilities, and food distribution centers actively hiring. 
      I-55 freight corridor expansion driving demand for CDL drivers and warehouse associates. 
      <a href="https://www.indeed.com/jobs?q=warehouse&l=Chicago%2C+IL+60632" target="_blank" style="color:var(--accent)">Indeed: Warehouse Jobs 60632 &rarr;</a>
    </span>
    <div style="margin-top:4px"><a href="https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiiwFBVV95cUxQR1YzUlBIWDk2VnVncTJ3dUJRSUE0T3ZJSGFmcFJGUWd6b0ZJVjVDQkpSS2VwU3ljbzJqazZYZnkxVlEyNU1xUlpyblV0S3FMN1FVS1JaeUM2bUlZMHdaOW0xZnpjV2ZfSFRHaEJZOGp5Zk9oUElDeXJ2OWc1bk40UGhKMG1vUUZSLVFj?oc=5" target="_blank" style="color:var(--accent)">Cool Stuff Made in the Chicago Area - Crain's Chicago Business</a></div>
  </li>
  <li style="margin-bottom:12px;padding-left:16px;border-left:3px solid #4a6cf7">
    <strong>Greater Chicago Food Depository</strong><br>
    <span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-secondary)">
      New facility expansion bringing 100+ jobs. Nonprofit roles in logistics, operations, and community outreach. 
      <a href="https://www.chicagosfoodbank.org/careers/" target="_blank" style="color:var(--accent)">GCFD Careers &rarr;</a>
    </span>
  </li>
</ul>
</div>
<h2 style="font-size:16px;font-weight:700;margin:24px 0 8px;padding-bottom:6px;border-bottom:2px solid var(--accent);color:var(--text-primary)">For Sale / Good Buys</h2>

<div style="margin:12px 0 20px">
<ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0">
  <li style="margin-bottom:12px;padding-left:16px;border-left:3px solid #ef4444">
    <strong>Industrial Properties</strong><br>
    <span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-secondary)">
      Sterling Bay expanding industrial division on Southwest Side. Multiple warehouse/light industrial 
      properties available in the 60632 corridor. 
      <a href="https://www.loopnet.com/search/commercial-real-estate/chicago-il/for-sale/?sk=60632" target="_blank" style="color:var(--accent)">LoopNet: 60632 Industrial For Sale &rarr;</a>
    </span>
    <div style="margin-top:4px"><a href="https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMioAFBVV95cUxQdUo3VXgyMVJvODdDay1IaXVpTTdwUVhtekd6MXdvM2JqTlllOVVFVUE5MklodFpRZE9FS3JZMzRTbjBvTjRNaGFOVmFSRG5aS2xYQ1JNQ0FoRkYtMFFONjRBM2V2UG4zd05RRXFoNF9kQ2FIdjduN3JqT0h6WFNhbEdzVy1TLWtIc0c1NUtKRnBlNTdhQUsxVnd5eXNoOGdG?oc=5" target="_blank" style="color:var(--accent)">TPG buys Cinespace, home of TV’s “Chicago Fire,” “Chicago Med” - The Real Deal</a></div>
  </li>
  <li style="margin-bottom:12px;padding-left:16px;border-left:3px solid #8b5cf6">
    <strong>Commercial Real Estate</strong><br>
    <span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-secondary)">
      Record property tax increases hitting South and West Sides hardest, potentially creating buying 
      opportunities. Cinespace film studio sale signals continued investor interest in Chicago industrial real estate. 
      <a href="https://www.crexi.com/properties?search=Chicago%2C+IL+60632" target="_blank" style="color:var(--accent)">Crexi: 60632 Listings &rarr;</a>
    </span>
    <div style="margin-top:4px"><a href="https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMimgFBVV95cUxQN0dLYlFSRUE4eWk0MDF2UEpEcUNaVHJsY0s4b2JDbkRxZ2NGajZFNWtkTnFsRmwwTjRxTkdQRVNEUURkeTdWbTVRZW9heHh3OVJOVzgzOXV2TjVxU1QxcWVqb19oa0c4Zks2U2lOd3pFS1o4NHhuNm9BS20xMFY1OFhnc1Fid3hTaFRKRUtIZzFrb01FSUg2YTd3?oc=5" target="_blank" style="color:var(--accent)">Marcus &amp; Millichap arranges $4M Sale of Texas Roadhouse ground lease property - Mainstreet Daily News Gainesville</a></div>
