</div>
<h2 style="font-size:16px;font-weight:700;margin:24px 0 8px;padding-bottom:6px;border-bottom:2px solid var(--accent);color:var(--text-primary)">For Rent</h2>

<div style="margin:12px 0 20px">
<ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0">
  <li style="margin-bottom:12px;padding-left:16px;border-left:3px solid #06b6d4">
    <strong>Industrial Space For Lease</strong><br>
    <span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-secondary)">
      Southwest Side business corridors receiving financial boost for Midway blight recovery. 
      Industrial flex space available near Archer &amp; Pulaski corridors at competitive rates. 
      <a href="https://www.loopnet.com/search/commercial-real-estate/chicago-il/for-lease/?sk=60632" target="_blank" style="color:var(--accent)">LoopNet: 60632 For Lease &rarr;</a>
    </span>
    <div style="margin-top:4px"><a href="https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMikAFBVV95cUxNVmJNc3VYVjFreHBNS1VlZWtETy1XdjVqNDFXWFVUWHBfSy1iSHVjc29CU2dUUjBXRjdqeW8zVk95M1EtYkw2M2ZNX0dVRzBpc3Fma0JhNE02T2N5Z1Z0M0p5MTJDN0FnTUZlbGlSSi0wX2t3d3l1R1F4MEljUzlIdnEwWjhIbDhnRUtDV2J3M2M?oc=5" target="_blank" style="color:var(--accent)">3457 W 55th St Ste G1, Chicago, IL 60632 - Realtor.com</a></div>
  </li>
  <li style="margin-bottom:12px;padding-left:16px;border-left:3px solid #ec4899">
    <strong>Commercial Storefronts</strong><br>
    <span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-secondary)">
      Retail spaces available along Archer Avenue and Pulaski Road. The Moving Archer Forward streetscape 
      improvements may increase foot traffic and retail viability in coming years.
      <a href="https://www.zillow.com/chicago-il-60632/rent/" target="_blank" style="color:var(--accent)">Zillow: 60632 Rentals &rarr;</a>
    </span>
    <div style="margin-top:4px"><a href="https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMixgFBVV95cUxPaGwtMV9IS2ctVUVLdG9PVlFBS1hJTm1lQU9QdVlSWmM5RnV5MjExa1REaFFoQ3VDT2RDS09wR3ZsN2M4dGMtQkYzZHdqaWNsZEhneDBnVV8tZVl5bVNPSk1jTFhOdktadUR4S04zbzc0NktHLV9yN1ZIOXJmeVdsNnd5TVhEU0tSaGxRbDZGMDZqdm1GWVlPR2NrOUFGUWN3V09tSkVFc0xHWlIwaUh3OTIyYjFCMjQxZFNzMGsxS3o0MDluY2c?oc=5" target="_blank" style="color:var(--accent)">Southwest Side Business Corridors Get Financial Boost To Recover From Midway Blitz - Block Club Chicago</a></div>
